Part A — Chatbase (chatbot that answers questions)
Go back to your Chatbase tab and do this:

Click Knowledge in the left menu
Click + Add source
Select File → upload your Excel/CSV sales file
Chatbase will read all your sales data
Now go to the chatbot preview on the right and type: "What is the total sales?" — it will answer from your data!



_______________________________________________
Go to zapier.com and create a new Zap:

Trigger → search Zapier Chatbots → select Chatbot Conversation Completed
Action → search Gmail → select Send Email
Fill in your email address in the "To" field
In the Body field, click + and select the chatbot conversation data
Click Publish


Step 3 — Connect the Zap back to Chatbase

After publishing the Zap in Zapier, copy the Zap ID or link
Come back to Chatbase → Logic → Run Zap
Paste the Zap ID there
Click Save
